OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPetrol costs push prices up
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fat fastest rate for 40     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fyears                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Prices are continuing to rise at their 
OL,6, fastest rate for more than 40 years,   
OL,7, driven by higher petrol and food costs.
OL,9,FUK inflation, the rate at which prices 
OL,10,Frise, jumped to 9.4% in the 12 months  
OL,11,Fto June from 9.1% in May, the Office   
OL,12,Ffor National Statistics (ONS) said.    
OL,14,FUnions have been calling for pay rises 
OL,15,Fto help workers cope as the rising cost
OL,16,Fof living means many are struggling    
OL,17,Fwith bills and turning to food banks.  
OL,19,FThe Bank of England has warned         
OL,20,Finflation will reach 11% this year.    
